== 雜記 ==
* 卡蘇里能夠說三種語言，[[英語|英語]]和[[法語|法語]]是外交行業的共通語言、此外他曾在[[劍橋大學|劍橋大學]]學習[[拉丁語|拉丁語]]
* 他有先天性足畸形
* 英語在國際會議公開使用始於1876年的柏林會議。

== 纪念及致敬 ==
以下是以罗伯特·斯图尔特，卡斯尔雷子爵名字命名的地點：

* {{le|卡斯爾雷 (新南威爾士州)|Castlereagh, New South Wales|卡斯爾雷}}，位於澳大利亞悉尼中心商業區西北方{{convert|67|km}}的郊區<ref name="lib.mq.edu.au">{{cite book |chapter-url=http://www.lib.mq.edu.au/all/journeys/1810/1810a/dec6.html |title=Journal of a Tour of Governor Macquarie's first Inspection of the Interior of the Colony Commencing on Tuesday the 6th. Novr. 1810 |first=Lachlan |last=Macquarie |chapter=Thursday 6th. Decr. |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091020032742/http://www.lib.mq.edu.au/all/journeys/1810/1810a/dec6.html |archive-date=2009-10-20 |via=[[Macquarie_University|Macquarie University]] |access-date=2020-02-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
* [[卡斯爾雷高速公路|卡斯爾雷高速公路]]，橫跨澳大利亞新南威爾士及昆士蘭兩州的內陸高速公路
* [[卡斯爾雷街|卡斯爾雷街]]，澳大利亞悉尼中心商業區的名店街<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cityofsydney.nsw.gov.au/learn/sydneys-history/people-and-places/streets |work=Sydney Streets |title=History of Sydney Streets |format=[[MS_Excel|MS Excel]] {{small|(for download)}} |publisher=[[City_of_Sydney|City of Sydney]] |date=4 December 2012 |access-date=13 January 2017 |archive-date=2020-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200202201420/https://www.cityofsydney.nsw.gov.au/learn/sydneys-history/people-and-places/streets |dead-url=no }}</ref>
* {{le|卡斯爾雷河|Castlereagh River}}，位於新南威尔士州中西部的河流<ref name=gnb>{{NSW GNR|id=JPKqoexOGH|title=Castlereagh River|date=22 April 1977|accessdate=18 January 2013}}</ref>

